Title: Gravitinos in non-Ricci-flat backgrounds

Authors: David Nolland (Durham U.)

Comments: LaTeX, 4 pages. Typos corrected, one significant

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B485 (2000) 308-310

We discuss the gauge invariance and "mass" of the Rarita-Schwinger field in abackground spacetime which is assumed to be Einstein but not necessarilyRicci-flat.